          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Targets were irradiated with a proton beam of energy",
                "between 2 and 4 MeV (in 200keV steps) with 600 nA for",
                "8 hours. the Ep=2.6 MeV irradiation was carried out",
                "with both accelerators and no difference in the cross",
                "section was found. The absolute number of target atoms",
                "and the uniformity were determined by the Rutherford",
                "Backscattering Method."
              ]
            }
          ],
